CMultiXSessionID Class Reference

List of all members.

Detailed Description

This class encapsulates the session ID type. Using this class and its operators, the basic type of session ID can be changed without changing the code. Current, the basic session ID is string.

Constructor & Destructor Documentation

CMultiXSessionID::CMultiXSessionID (  )  [inline]

Default constructor.

Create a SessionID object with an empty string. This implies an empty session ID. No session can have an empty session ID. To make a session object a valid one, its SessionID should not be empty.
